# SEO for Landing Pages

## Meta Tags (Every Page)

- `<title>` – unique, descriptive, ~50–60 chars
- `<meta name="description">` – ~155–160 chars, keywords
- `<meta name="keywords">` – relevant terms ( formación belleza, uñas, cejas, estética, Vigo )
- `<link rel="canonical">` – absolute URL
- `lang="es"` on `<html>`

## Open Graph

- `og:title`, `og:description`, `og:image`, `og:url`, `og:type`, `og:locale`
- Twitter: `twitter:card`, `twitter:title`, `twitter:description`, `twitter:image`

## JSON-LD Schema

- **Organization** – name, url, logo
- **LocalBusiness** – address, telephone, email
- **EducationalOrganization** – courses
- **Review** – for testimonials (aggregate rating, individual)

## Images

- All images must have descriptive `alt` attribute
- Placeholders: use `aria-label` or `role="img"` with descriptive text
- When real images: add `width`, `height`, `loading="lazy"` for below-fold

## Semantic HTML

- Single `<h1>` per page (brand)
- Logical h2/h3 hierarchy
- `<header>`, `<main>`, `<section>`, `<footer>`
